(1) 使用 Flask / FastAPI 架設 API
from fastapi import FastAPI
import joblib

app = FastAPI()
model = joblib.load('model.pkl')

@app.post("/predict")
def predict(data: dict):
    X = [data['feature1'], data['feature2']]
    y_pred = model.predict([X])
    return {"prediction": y_pred.tolist()}

啟動後 → curl 或前端即可呼叫

curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/predict -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"feature1": 3, "feature2": 7}'

(2) Streamlit / Gradio：快速建立互動介面
import streamlit as st
import joblib

model = joblib.load('model.pkl')

x1 = st.number_input('Feature 1')
x2 = st.number_input('Feature 2')
if st.button('Predict'):
    pred = model.predict([[x1, x2]])
    st.write('Prediction:', pred[0])

👉 適合 Demo、內部展示或教育用途。

